<ReactFlow
  nodes={enriched}
  edges={edges.map((e) => ({
    ...e,
    type: "smoothstep",
    animated: true,
    style: { strokeWidth: 2, stroke: "#8884d8" },
  }))}
  nodeTypes={nodeTypes}
  onNodeClick={handleNodeClick}
  fitView
  fitViewOptions={{ padding: 0.4 }}
  onInit={(instance) => {
    if (rfInstanceRef) rfInstanceRef.current = instance;
  }}
>
  <Background />
  <MiniMap />
  <Controls />
</ReactFlow>
